data.description:
THIS IS A GREAT OPPORTUNITY TO OWN A HOME IN SEABROOKE.  THIS HOME OFFERS, SOLID BLOCK CONSTRUCTION, IN-GROUND SCREEN COVERED SALT WATER POOL, 3 BEDROOMS, 2 FULL BATHS, 2 CAR ATTACHED GARAGE, VAULTED CEILINGS, LARGE OPEN KITCHEN AND A BIG FAMILY ROOM WITH A WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE.  THE KITCHEN HAS LOTS OF CABINETS, ALL NEW STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, NEW GRANITE COUNTER TOPS, A BREAKFAST/SNACK BAR AND AN EATING AREA.  THE FORMAL LIVING ROOM AND FORMAL DINING ROOM ARE WONDERFUL FOR ENTERTAINING FRIENDS.  YOU WILL LOVE THE CONVENIENCE OF THE UTILITY/MUD ROOM.  
NEW ROOF 2016, NEW TRANE HVAC SYSTEM 2016, REFINISHED AND CONVERTED SALT WATER POOL 2017, ALL NEW TILE FLOORS 2017, NEW BATH REMODEL 2016, NEW ELECTRIC 2017, DOG FRIENDLY FENCED YARD, 2017.

PLAN TO VIEW THIS HOME TODAY!
data.whatILove: PERFECT NEIGHBORHOOD WITH AMAZING PARK ACROSS THE STREET. CLOSE TO TAMPA AND BEACHES. JUST A FEW MORE FINAL TOUCHES AND THIS AMAZING HOME WILL BE READY TO TOUR.
